HEADWORD: Dail
<hw>Dail</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the lower house of the parliament of
the Republic of Ireland; -- also called the <altname>Dail
Eirann</altname>. From its members is selected the <er>Taoiseach</er>,
or prime minister.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Dail Eireann.</syn>⟦br⟧
